    "            \"org.apache.hadoop:hadoop-aws:3.3.4,com.amazonaws:aws-java-sdk-bundle:1.12.262\") \\\n",
    "    .config(\"spark.hadoop.fs.s3a.endpoint\", \"http://minio:9000\") \\\n",
